video.title: The Princess Weiyoung
video.synopsis: A princess descended from a ruined noble family disguises herself as the woman who saved her life and embarks on a mission to avenge her loved ones.

episodes.synopsis: A princess of Liang is born in the time of the Northern and Southern dynasties. Years later, her father returns home from his confinement.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: The collapsed Xin'er is saved by the kind-hearted Li Wei Young, who lives her life in obscurity despite being the daughter of the noble Li Xiaoran.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Chiyun Rou controls the Li family with her arrogant daughter Changle. Wei Young surprises everyone at a birthday celebration for the grandmother.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Chiyun Rou feels Changle's position threatened and plots a devious trap for Wei Young by laying blame for all the misfortune at the estate upon her.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: After being saved by the man running from killers, Wei Young is nursed back to health, glad to be reunited with Tuoba Jun who has now saved her twice.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young is back at the Li estate and glad to see that her grandmother and mother are well. Tuoba Jun waits for her at the appointed place.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: While attending a celebration along with Changle and Changru, Wei Young is reunited with Tuoba Jun but is shocked to learn his real identity.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young is worried she will be discovered when Li Minfeng gets his hands a portrait of the Liang princess. She sneaks into his room to retrieve it.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Changle takes her anger out on Wei Young, thinking she is getting to close too Tuoba Jun. Then Changle takes credit for Wei Young's relief plan.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young takes a risk by telling the Crown Princess that there is a problem with the plan, but Minfeng goes ahead with it, leading to violence.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Minfeng and Changle are handed down punishment after Wei Young proves that it was she and not Changle who came up with the plan.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young vows revenge after Minfeng causes Ziyan to meet her untimely end. She exposes his wrongdoing at a celebration held in her honor.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Revenge against Wei Young burns in Chiyun Rou's heart as she mourns her son Minfeng. She comes up with a plan after learning Wei Young's secret.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: When Wei Young's identity is put to the test, she realizes it's the work of Chiyun Rou and tries to outmaneuver her, but proof is brought against her.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Li Minde heads out to Zhengding in his uncle's stead. As Tuoba Di tags along with him pretending to be a prince, they are followed.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Xiaoran thinks that Chiyun Rou concocted a story, but then seeing proof of her illness begins to doubt Wei Young and confines her to quarters.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun saves Wei Young from being killed in the nick of time, and tells everyone that the fan is his. Later he declares his feelings to Wei Young.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Yu tries to bring Wei Young to his side after seeing her stand up to Tuoba Han, Changle and Changxi when they abuse Minde.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: At a banquet for the Empress, Wei Young gives Li Changru the opportunity to dance before the assembly, then performs with Tuoba Jun and Minde.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Minde has been attacked and it's not clear whether he is still alive. Zhou Xuemei realizes Chiyun Rou is behind it and places her hope in Wei Young.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Di comes with Tuoba Jun to the Li home and visits Lady Zhou, while Tuoba Jun gently comforts Wei Young. Minde escapes death and returns home.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Minde tries to kill Chiyun Rou to avenge Lady Zhou. Wei Young and Jun Tao learn that Jun Tao's father Ming Shu and other Jiang vassals are in danger.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: The Jiang vassals are released thanks to Tuoba Jun, but Chiyun Nan appears and slaughters them. Ming Shu escapes and later gives Wei Young a document.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: The Emperor holds a hunting expedition and declares he will grant the top hunter one request. Meanwhile Changru plots to ruin Changle's reputation.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young wants to win the hunting contest so she can reveal Chiyun Nan's treason to the Emperor. Tuoba Jun goes missing on the final day of the hunt.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young exits the scene so Tuoba Jun will not know that she helped him. Changle climbs down into the pit and lies that she is Jun's savior.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun comes to the rescue when Wei Young is beset by Chiyun Nan's men and chased to a precipice, but Wei Young does not want to get him involved.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: With her sights on Tuoba Jun, Changle finds favor with the Crown Princess. Wei Young has nothing to hide from Tuoba Jun as they declare their love.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: While Tuoba Jun is caught in a dilemma with talk of marriage to Changle, the Emperor decides on an arranged marriage for Wei Young to avoid conflict.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun earns the wrath of the Emperor and is stripped of his title for going after Wei Young, who is assaulted by the Song envoy near the border.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Yu follows Wei Young as she heads for Huatai, which is encircled by the Song army. Wei Young is reunited with Tuoba Jun after her plan succeeds.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun recovers from his comatose state thanks to Wei Young's tender care. Changru feels anger and sorrow because of Wei Young's gift to Tuoba Yu.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young suspects foul play behind Tuoba Jun's injury when Tuoba Yu is honored instead of him. She later receives a letter that startles her.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: The Crown Princess is killed while Wei Young is out following the cryptic letter. Wei Young gets accused, and even Tuoba Jun begins to doubt her.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young proves her innocence and lays Chiyun Nan's guilt bare before the Emperor, who forces her to give up on both her revenge and Tuoba Jun.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: After receiving a warm reception from the Emperor, Tuoba Yu learns about Changru's plot while he was away and is asked by Tuoba Jun to help Wei Young.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young, now a servant, is shocked to hear that Jun will take Changle as his bride. Even worse, she is forced to attend the ceremony.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: After removing Tuoba Jun from the succession fight, Tuoba Yu plots against Tuoba Han. Jun looks into his mother's death and begins to suspect Changle.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: A poisoned needle is discovered in the clothing of the Empress. Wei Young is falsely accused and given three days to prove her innocence.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young cleverly reveals the real culprit and is then put in charge of the other maids as a reward. Tuoba Jun continues to hide his feelings.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: The Emperor strips Tuoba Han of his title and puts him into confinement when his sins are revealed. Wei Young has doubts that Changle killed Baizhi.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: A delegation from the Khanate arrives. Minde comes before the Emperor with his sister and Jiao, who proposes a marriage between the Khan and Tuoba Di.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: Princess Anle sees Wei Young as her sworn enemy. When the body of the princess is later found down a well, Wei Young falls under suspicion.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun appears before Wei Young, who will be killed in three days time, and tells her everything. Wei Young realizes how he had been protecting her.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Wei Young is picked by the Emperor to be his lady-in-waiting and spends time with Tuoba Jun while Changru is held at the palace until she gives birth.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Minde is badly wounded by Tuoba Yu after infiltrating the military office, but heads to the palace and saves Wei Young from poison without her knowing.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: The Emperor is displeased with Wei Young for setting Tuoba Jun and Tuoba Yu against each other. Changru tells Changle about her husband's rendezvous.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: When Changu's plot against Wei Young is revealed she is sentenced to be killed after giving birth. Tuoba Jun receives a letter about his father.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: In Wei Young's investigation of Zhong Zheng's murder she searches his manor and finds a secret room, only to become trapped inside with Tuoba Yu.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun discovers that Tuoba Yu was pulling the strings behind Zhong Zheng's murder. He uses Changle to draw out the culprit Chiyun Nan.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Jun goes with Wei Young back to the manor to investigate and finds evidence of his father's innocence, which he reports to the Emperor.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Tuoba Yu holds the Li family hostage and forces Wei Young to lie about the Emperor's choice of heir. Tuoba Jun is arrested for treason and tortured.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Convinced that Tuoba Jun has lost his mind, Tuoba Yu lets him go. Changle plans to have Changru take the blame for poisoning Wei Young.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: After giving Wei Young the only antidote pill, Tuoba Jun coughs up blood and collapses. Changru appears with sword in hand and moves toward Wei Young.
episodes.title: Episode 54
